                "invention-title": [
                    "Ammonia and methanol pyrolysis gas blending combustion engine system",
                    "一种氨与甲醇裂解气掺烧的发动机系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of internal combustion engines, and discloses an ammonia and methanol pyrolysis gas blending combustion engine system. Comprising a methanol storage tank, a methanol heater, a methanol injector, a methanol cracker, a tail gas heating pipe, a methanol cracking gas pump, a methanol cracking gas injector, an ignition device, an ammonia injector, an engine, an ammonia storage tank, an ammonia high-pressure common rail, an electronic control unit (ECU) and a tail gas emptying pipe. The methanol is catalytically cracked by using waste heat of the waste gas, so that the waste heat energy of the waste gas is recovered, the hydrogen-containing cracked gas can be prepared, and the combustion process of ammonia fuel is optimized. Directly spraying pyrolysis gas containing methanol steam, hydrogen, carbon monoxide and other components into a gas inlet channel of the engine to form premixed gas of pyrolysis gas/air; the ammonia fuel is mixed with pyrolysis gas for combustion through in-cylinder direct injection; the injection amount of ammonia and cracking gas is adjusted according to the load requirement of the engine and the conditions such as the methanol catalytic cracking rate at different exhaust temperatures, and efficient low-emission combustion of the engine under various working conditions is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于内燃机技术领域，公开一种氨与甲醇裂解气掺烧的发动机系统，包括甲醇储罐、甲醇加热器、甲醇喷油器、甲醇裂解器、尾气加热管、甲醇裂解气泵、甲醇裂解气喷油器、点火装置、氨喷油器、发动机、氨储罐、氨高压共轨、电控单元ECU和尾气排空管。本发明利用废气余热催化裂解甲醇，不仅回收废气的余热能量，还能制备含氢气裂解气，优化氨燃料的燃烧过程。具体是将含有甲醇蒸汽、氢气、一氧化碳和其他组分的裂解气直接喷入发动机的进气道内，形成裂解气/空气的预混合气；氨燃料通过缸内直喷喷射与裂解气混合燃烧；根据发动机负荷需求和不同排气温度下甲醇催化裂解率等条件来调节氨和裂解气的喷射量，实现发动机在各个工况下的高效低排燃烧。"
                }
